<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.5">
<l>ārā vamutamā yallāvi yuḷkalanta</l>
<l>kārār karumukilpō leṉṉammāṉ kaṇṇaṉukku</l>
<l>nērāvāy cempavaḷaṅ kaṇpātaṅ kaikamalam</l>
<l>pērāra nīṇmuṭināṇ piṉṉu miḻaipalavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On Kṛṣṇa, my lord like a black cloud full of rain</l>
<l>who mingled with [my] dark soul, being never-sating ambrosia,</l>
<l>red coral does not match [his] mouth, [nor] lotus [his] eye, hands, feet;</l>
<l>many are [his] jewels, moreover a string, a tall crown, a big garland.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
